1.
Curl -O http://production.cf.rubygems.org/rubygems/rubygems-1.8.25.tgz

2.
tar xvzf rubygems-1.8.25.tgz

3.
cd rubygems-1.8.25

4.
ruby setup.rb config
ruby setup.rb setup
ruby setup.rb install

